[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    111[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Step 1 (ingest_rxnorm):** Pseudocode parses RRF files and creates drug nodes with UPSERT. Python uses MERGE (Neptune's equivalent of upsert) with the same properties. Python adds relationship loading as Step 1b, which the pseudocode covers in the same function. Consistent.
